elated with the  model  sport utility vehicle related with the  model  a boxed set of  vehicles were produced the emergency truck related with the  model the toy truck and helicopter related with the  model and the monster truck related with the  model note this is only available through the hess toy truck website referencesedit  matt krantz march    companies cut the most jobs in    httpwwwhesscomcompany  httpbetafortunecomfortunelistfilteredsearchbynamehess  httpwwwhesscomcompanyhesshistory  httpwwwhartreepartnerscomabout  httpwwwhesscomoperationsoperationsmap  hoovers handbook of american business  volume  hoovers  pp – isbn    benedict roger w may   merger of amerada petroleum hess oil valued at  billion voted by holders the wall street journal pg   court rules ameradas holders were misled in merger with hess august   the wall street journal p   metro business amerada hess to expand bloomberg news  february  – via the new york times   mote dave triton energy corporation answerscom retrieved    amerada hess to acquire triton energy for  per share in cash press release amerada hess  retrieved    craver richard september   speedway conversion of triad wilcohess stores under way winstonsalem journal retrieved september     hess corporation investor relations annual reports phxcorporateirnet retrieved    amerada hess changes name to hess corporation and announces threeforone stock split companys stock to commence trading under symbol hes on may    closure of hess port reading refinery means layoffs for  employees njcom   hess announces culmination of transformation into pure play ep company httpphxcorporateirnetphoenixzhtmlcpirolnewsarticleidhighlight  announced closure of hess corps port reading refinery not seen having major impact on gasoline markets httpwwweurasiareviewcomannouncedclosureofhesscorpsportreadingrefinerynotseenhavingmajorimpactongasolinemarketsanalysis  de la merced michael j new york times hess to sell gas stations as part of a shift in strategy ma